    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it is a total gem! It's been kept in absolutely pristine condition and looks just like it did the day it left the showroom. I've babied this ride since day one, so it's super clean inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
