    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This specimen features the 3.8L DFI flat-six, producing 385 hp and 310 lb-ft of torque, paired with a rare 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is dialed in with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional corner-exit telemetry. This vehicle is free of bore scoring and IMS concerns typical of earlier generations. Maintenance is current, including a recent overhaul of the cooling system and spark plug replacement. The exterior retains factory-spec paint depth with no swirl marks, and the interior exhibits zero bolster wear. A mechanically flawless, turn-key example for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
